{"tid":124152,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"校園賭博漫畫《狂賭之淵》宣布將製作動畫！","createTime":"2017-02-17T11:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T15:43:04.000Z","uid":51665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f28f52ab22f254cdbd7691e03b1e1003ab92654","tid":124152,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"由河本ほむら原作、尚村透作畫的校園賭博漫畫《狂賭之淵》於2014年開始連載，因漫畫裡描寫賭博相關事物、細膩探討人類心理以及讓讀者看了有快感的顏藝，一出單行本就引起不小話題。《狂賭之淵》於今日宣布將製作動畫，想必粉絲們已經等不及想快點看動畫了吧！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.animen.com.tw/FilesUpload/CK-Images/20170217_94_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animen.com.tw%2FFilesUpload%2FCK-Images%2F20170217_94_02.jpg&h=59cc1ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《狂賭之淵》動畫將由動畫製作公司「MAPPA」製作，MAPPA近期的作品有最近話題不斷的《Yuri!!! on ICE》、《牙狼〈GARO〉-炎之刻印-》、《東京殘響》以及將在台灣上映的動畫電影《這個世界的角落》；監督則是由「林祐一郎」擔任。<br />\n<br />\n對於製作動畫一事，河本ほむら表示這項消息是人生最大的驚訝，現在就很期待夢子、芽亞里、鈴井會以什麼模樣動起來、會以什麼聲音說話。今後《狂賭之淵》的動畫與原作也請大家多多指教；尚村透則是非常感謝大家，一想到自己能看到漫畫裡的場景，宛如像在作夢一樣，體內的被虐狂之心現在興奮不已！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.animen.com.tw/FilesUpload/CK-Images/20170217_94_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animen.com.tw%2FFilesUpload%2FCK-Images%2F20170217_94_03.jpg&h=95661c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事描述「私立百花王學園」是一所以賭博能力決定地位高低的名門學校，主角「蛇喰夢子」是位神秘的轉學美少女，雖然外表看似優雅，事實上是一位賭狂，只要聽到賭博相關事情就會相當興奮且也擅長賭博。而在私立百花王學園裡，只要賭博贏了就能享受天堂待遇，輸了則宛如下地獄。夢子轉來這所學校是否會帶來劇烈影響呢&hellip;？一場賭博心理戰就此展開。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.animen.com.tw/FilesUpload/CK-Images/20170217_94_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animen.com.tw%2FFilesUpload%2FCK-Images%2F20170217_94_04.jpg&h=9fa31521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290b667d5b817f191ee72d3cea8d8946c3b47407","tid":124152,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea64e587411039ca334daed96bedb6edae5bac2","tid":124152,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"故事賭法同鋪排都唔好睇<br />\n唯一賣點係表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87847f8f17671b2e9aae9e93530db72ed20199a","tid":124152,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"下年?"},{"pid":"4272158272ed92f2a2b2388ee36d5043e13e29d2","tid":124152,"uid":68284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:45:43.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套野幾好睇"},{"pid":"22c1e5201ccfb155ba63e53da96b0bab5c556c53","tid":124152,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>故事賭法同鋪排都唔好睇<br />\n唯一賣點係表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9賭法"},{"pid":"f4f34e7fe9db3b28c23e92cfc3f07f55d77c90d4","tid":124152,"uid":43760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:51:13.000Z","msg":"第一話已經開始睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efac8580e0347095366dcce7c6b2cf316df6c96","tid":124152,"uid":43760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"夢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a52c0e7c04b1fb5365f2799d23929603894c692","tid":124152,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi